Package Order

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InvoiceCtrl
    A control class that mediates between OrderInvoice entity objects and the InvoiceUI boundary object.
    InvoiceUI
    A boundary class that interfaces with the application user for invoice related functions.
    Order
    Represents an order made by customers (represented by tables) in the restaurant.
    OrderCtrl
    A control class that mediates between Order entity objects and the OrderUI boundary object.
    OrderInvoice
    Represents an order invoice of an order.
    OrderUI
    A boundary class that interfaces with the application user for order related functions.
